            <div class="text-left mt-4 terms-text px-3">
                <h2 class="mt-4 mb-2">Why to Take a Selfie?</h2>
                <p>Ensuring the safety of our users is our highest priority. In certain areas, we request that your
                     complete liveness checks to help us confirm that you are a genuine person. Additionally, we may perform identity verification to prevent the use of our services by individuals who may pose a risk.
                     These checks also help secure your account and prevent identity theft.</p>
                <p>We appreciate your cooperation and support in making SheDrives a safer platform for everyone.</p>

                <h2 class="mt-4 mb-2">How to Take a Selfie?</h2>
                <p>When prompted, take a real-time image of yourself using the app, following the on-screen instructions. The instructions will be provided as text and animations. If the real-time image is of you,
                   the verification process should be smooth, allowing you to place your first order.</p>
                <h3>Key Tips:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Make sure you are in a well-lit area</li>
                    <li>Ensure your face and neck are within the white frame lines</li>
                    <li>Keep your eyes uncovered</li>
                    <li>Avoid wearing a mask, hat, or sunglasses</li>
                    <li>Hold your phone steady at arm’s length to prevent blurriness</li>
                    <li>Do not capture an existing photo or an image of someone/something else</li>
                    <p>It’s essential that you capture a real-time photo of yourself and not a photo of an existing image or someone else, as this will result in a failed verification.</p>

                </ul>

                <h2 class="mt-4 mb-2">How Often Will I Be Asked to Complete a Liveness Check?</h2>
                <p>You will only be asked to complete the liveness check once. If you’ve already passed this check but are being prompted again,
                   it might be because you completed it on a different account.</p>

                <h2 class="mt-4 mb-2">How Is My Photo Processed and Stored?</h2>
                <p>When you take a selfie in the app, we receive it and share it with our liveness check service provider. Our provider has assured us that they do not store any photos after the liveness check processing is complete.
                    All photos are securely stored on our servers, and we do not share your photo with other users.</p>
                <p>To protect your account’s security, we will retain your photo as long as you maintain an account with us, in accordance with local laws and our Privacy Policy. After this period, your photo will be deleted.</p>
                <p>We may disclose your photo for legal reasons, as outlined in our Privacy Policy.</p>

                <h2 class="mt-4 mb-2">What Happens If My Liveness Check Fails?</h2>
                <p>If your photo doesn’t pass the check, please try again, following our guidelines (‘How Do I Take a Selfie?’). You can also try restarting your device. The number of attempts is unlimited. However, you will not be able to place an order in our app until you successfully complete the check.</p>

                <h2 class="mt-4 mb-2">Ask Questions or Request a Review </h2>
                <p>If you have any questions regarding these checks, or if you are unable to pass the check and believe this may be an error,
                    please contact our user support at <a class="text-grey" href="https://SheDrivesapp.com/contacts/support.">https://SheDrivesapp.com/contacts/support.</a></p>

            </div>
